{"prepare":{"headline":"Artikelvorbereitung","fields":{"checkout":{"label":"Idealo Checkout","desc":"Activate Idealo Checkout in order to receive orders from Idealo and synchronize order status in your shop.","key":"_#_platform_#_.checkout.status","type":"checkbox","values":{"val":"apply Checkout for all selected products"},"default":{"val":false},"submit":"Checkout.Enabled"},"shippingmethods":{"label":"Shipping Method","desc":"Shipping method is only applied if you activate Idealo Checkout. <br> You will be able to specify which shipping method you are using for specific product.","key":"_#_platform_#_.shipping.methods","type":"selection","values":null},"paymentmethods":{"label":"Payment Method","desc":"Payment method is only applied if you activate Idealo Checkout. <br> You will be able to specify which payment method you want to be used for specific product.","key":"_#_platform_#_.payment.methods","type":"selection","values":null}}},"lang":{"headline":"Spracheinstellungen","fields":{"lang":{"label":"Artikelbeschreibung","key":"_#_platform_#_.lang","type":"selection","values":null}}},"checkin":{"headline":"Artikel hochladen: Voreinstellungen","fields":{"0":{"label":"Statusfilter","key":"_#_platform_#_.checkin.status","type":"checkbox","values":{"val":"nur aktive Artikel &uuml;bernehmen"},"default":{"val":false}},"mfnpartno":{"label":"Manufacturer Part Number","desc":"If you use a contribution to manage the manufacturer part number in a special database field, you can select the used database table and column here. By this setting, the proper field will be prefilled during the item preparing process. <br \/><br \/>If the column \"products_id\" uses another field name, please enter the alternative description of the used column. <br \/><br \/>Hint: These settings will not be verified. If they are erroneous, database errors will occur!","key":"comparisonshopping.checkin.manufacturerpartnumber.table","type":"dbfieldselector","expertsetting":true,"morefields":{"alias":{"label":"<span class=\"tt\">`products_id`<\/span> Alias","key":"comparisonshopping.checkin.manufacturerpartnumber.alias","type":"text","cssClasses":["autoWidth"]}}}}},"credentials":{"headline":"Order Import","fields":{"credentials":{"label":"Credentials for Idealo Checkout","desc":"Please enter your token from Idealo.","key":"_#_platform_#_.checkout.token","type":"text","submit":"Checkout.Token"}}},"orders":{"headline":" ","fields":{"doimport":{"label":"Activate Import ","desc":"Should orders from _#_platformName_#_ be imported? <br\/><br\/>\n                           Orders are imported automatically every hour as the default setting.<br><br>\n                           You can adjust the import-time individually, by configuring <br>\n                           \"magnalister admin\" &rarr; \"Global Configuration\" &rarr; \"Orders Import\".<br><br>\n                           You can manually import orders, by clicking the assigned button in the magnalister-header, next left to the ant-logo.<br><br>\n                           Additionally, you can call order imports by setting a own cronjob to your following shop-link:<br>\n                           <i>http:\/\/www.YourShop.com\/magnaCallback.php?do=ImportOrders<\/i><br><br>\n                           Setting an own cronjob is permitted for customers within the service plan \"Flat\", only.<br><br>\n                           Own cronjob-calls, exceeding a quarter of an hour, or calls from customers, who are not within the service plan \"Flat\", will be blocked.\n                           ","key":"_#_platform_#_.import","type":"radio","values":{"true":"Yes","false":"No"},"default":"true","submit":"Orders.Import","morefields":{"preimportsince":{"label":"First-time order-import","desc":"The date, an order import will be processed the first time.","key":"_#_platform_#_.preimport.start","type":"date","default":"now","submit":"Orders.Import.Start","cssClasses":["autoWidth","rightSpacer"]}}},"onlycomplete":false,"customersgroup":{"label":"Customer Group","desc":"Allocate customers from _#_platformName_#_ to a customer group of the shop.","key":"_#_platform_#_.CustomerGroup","type":"selection","values":null,"default":"2"},"unpaidsatus":false,"openstatus":{"label":"Order Status","desc":"Status set for an imported _#_platformName_#_ order.","key":"_#_platform_#_.orderstatus.open","type":"selection","values":null,"default":"2"},"defaultshipping":{"label":"Shipping Method of Orders","desc":"Versandart, die allen _#_platformName_#_-Bestellungen zugeordnet wird. Standard: \"marketplace\".<br><br>\n                           Diese Einstellung ist wichtig f&uuml;r den Rechnungs- und Lieferscheindruck und f&uuml;r die nachtr&amul;gliche\n                           Bearbeitung der Bestellung im Shop sowie einige Warenwirtschaften.","key":"_#_platform_#_.orderimport.shippingmethod","type":"selection","values":{"textfield":"From Textfield"},"default":"textfield","expertsetting":true,"morefields":{"quantity":{"key":"_#_platform_#_.orderimport.shippingmethod.name","type":"text","default":"marketplace","cssClasses":["autoWidth"]}}},"defaultpayment":{"label":"Payment Method of Orders","desc":"Zahlart, die allen _#_platformName_#_-Bestellungen zugeordnet wird. Standard: \"marketplace\".<br><br>\n                           Diese Einstellung ist wichtig f&uuml;r den Rechnungs- und Lieferscheindruck und f&uuml;r die nachtr&amul;gliche\n                           Bearbeitung der Bestellung im Shop sowie einige Warenwirtschaften.","key":"_#_platform_#_.orderimport.paymentmethod","type":"selection","values":{"textfield":"From Textfield"},"default":"textfield","expertsetting":true,"morefields":{"quantity":{"key":"_#_platform_#_.orderimport.paymentmethod.name","type":"text","default":"marketplace","cssClasses":["autoWidth"]}}}}},"vat":{"headline":"","desc":"<b>V.A.T.<b>","fields":{"vat_unknown":{"label":"V.A.T. for Items, not Listed in the Shop","desc":"If the item is not listed by magnalister, V.A.T. can not be determined.<br\/>\n                           As a solution, the V.A.T. value added here, will be inserted for all items, that are not listed in the shop.","hint":"V.A.T. in percentage: Inserted for _#_platformName_#_-items, that are not listed in the shop.","key":"_#_platform_#_.mwst.fallback","type":"text","default":"19","verify":"float"}}},"orderSyncState":{"headline":"","desc":"<b>Synchronisation of order status from shop to _#_platformName_#_<\/b>","fields":{"syncstatus":{"label":"Status Synchronisation","desc":"<dl>\n                                <dt>Automatic Synchronisation by CronJob (recommended)<\/dt>\n                                    <dd>The function \"Automatic Synchronisation by CronJob\" sends each 2 hours the current shipment state to _#_platformName_#_.<br\/>\n                                        It takes the values from the shop's database, no matter whether you have changed it manually or by an external tool (like an ERP).<br\/><br\/>\n                                        You can trigger a synchonisation every time by pressing the \"Synchronise order status\" button in the upper right corner of tha magnalister plugin.<br \/><br \/>\n                                        Additionally, you can use an own cronjob (if you have a Flat account, up to each 15 minutes), by executing the following link:<br\/><br\/>\n                                        <i>http:\/\/www.YourShop.de\/magnaCallback.php?do=SyncOrderStatus<\/i><br\/><br\/>\n                                        Cronjobs of Users without the Flat tarif, or when more often than each 15 minutes, will be blocked.\n                                    <\/dd>\n                            <\/dl>\n                ","key":"_#_platform_#_.orderstatus.sync","type":"selection","values":{"auto":"Automatic Synchronisation by CronJob (recommended)","no":"No synchronization"},"default":"no"},"shippedstatus":{"label":"Confirm shipment with","desc":"Set the state of the order in your shop, that represents the marketplaces \"Shipped\" state.","key":"ebay.orderstatus.shipped","type":"selection","values":null},"carrier":{"label":"Carrier","desc":"Vorausgew&auml;hlter Spediteur beim Best&auml;tigen des Versandes nach _#_platformName_#_","key":"_#_platform_#_.orderstatus.carrier.default","expertsetting":true,"type":"text","values":null},"carrierMatch":{"label":"Carrier Matching","key":"_#_platform_#_.orderstatus.carrier.dbmatching.table","desc":"If you use a contribution to manage your tracking codes and carriers, you can select the used database table and column here.\n                           By this setting, the field for the carrier will be prefilled by the value of the used database field. Alternateively the setting from <b>Carrier<\/b> will be used.<br\/><br\/>\n                           If \"orders_id\" is using another field name, please enter the alias for the alternative description.<br \/><br \/>\n                           Hint: These settings will not be verified. If they are erroneous, database errors will occur!","type":"dbfieldselector","expertsetting":true,"morefields":{"alias":{"label":"<span class=\"tt\">`orders_id`<\/span> Alias","key":"_#_platform_#_.orderstatus.carrier.dbmatching.alias","type":"text","cssClasses":["autoWidth"]}}},"trackingMatch":{"label":"Trackingcode Matching","key":"_#_platform_#_.orderstatus.trackingcode.dbmatching.table","desc":"If you use a contribution to manage your tracking codes, here you can select the used database table and column. By this setting, the field for the tracking code will be prefilled by the value of the used database field.<br\/><br\/>If \"orders_id\" is using another field name, please enter the alias for the alternative description.<br \/><br \/>Hint: These settings will not be verified. If they are erroneous, database errors will occur!","type":"dbfieldselector","expertsetting":true,"morefields":{"alias":{"label":"<span class=\"tt\">`orders_id`<\/span> Alias","key":"_#_platform_#_.orderstatus.trackingcode.dbmatching.alias","type":"text","cssClasses":["autoWidth"]}}},"cancelstatus":{"label":"Cancel Order with","desc":"Set the state of the order in your shop, that represents the marketplaces \"Cacelled\" state.","key":"_#_platform_#_.orderstatus.cancelled","type":"selection","values":null},"cancelreaason":{"label":"Cancel Order reason","desc":"Please select default cancellation reason","key":"_#_platform_#_.orderstatus.cancelreason","type":"selection","values":null},"cancelcomment":{"label":"Cancel Order comment","desc":"You can add your default comment for canceling order.","key":"_#_platform_#_.orderstatus.cancelcomment","type":"text"}}},"inventoryupdate":{"headline":"Synchronisation of Inventory","desc":"Defines the product properties, that will be updated automatically on _#_platformName_#_.","fields":[{"label":"Product Price","desc":"<dl>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<dt>Automatic Synchronisation by CronJob (recommended)<\/dt>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<dd>The function \"Automatic Synchronisation by CronJob\" equalizes the current shop-price with the Amazon-price every 4 hours (starts at 0 pm).<br \/><br \/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t    By this procedure, the database values are checked for changes. The new data will be submitted, also when the changes had been set\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t    by an inventory management system.<br><br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t    You can manually synchronize price changes, by clicking the assigned button in the magnalister-header, next left to the ant-logo.<br><br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t    Additionally, you can synchronize price changes, by setting a own cronjob to your following shop-link:<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t    <i>http:\/\/www.YourShop.com\/magnaCallback.php?do=SyncInventory<\/i><br><br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t    Setting an own cronjob is permitted for customers within the service plan \"Flat\", only.<br><br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t    Own cronjob-calls, exceeding a quarter of an hour, or calls from customers, who are not within the service plan \"Flat\", will be blocked.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<dt>Item editing sets Amazon-price identical to shop-price.<\/dt>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<dd>If the price will be changed by editing the item in the shop-admin-panel, the new price will be submitted to Amazon automatically.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br>Changes, that will be set in the database only (e.g. by an inventory management system), will <b>not<\/b> be captured and submitted!<\/dd>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/dl><br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b>Notice:<\/b> Settings in \"Configuration\" &rarr; \"Price Calculation\" will be provided.","key":"_#_platform_#_.inventorysync.price","type":"selection","values":{"auto":"Automatic Synchronisation by CronJob (recommended)","no":"No synchronization"},"default":"auto"}]},"stats":{"headline":"Statistikeinstellungen","fields":{"mtlcost":{"label":"Monatliche Grundgeb&uuml;hr","desc":"Sollten keine monatlichen Geb&uuml;hren f&auml;llig werden, geben Sie in das Feld \"0.0\" ein.","key":"_#_platform_#_.cost.montly","type":"text","default":"0.0","verify":"float","cssClasses":["autoWidth"],"rightlabel":"const(DEFAULT_CURRENCY)","formatstr":"%.2f"},"clickcost":{"label":"Kosten pro Klick","desc":"Sollten keine Kosten pro Klick entstehen, geben Sie in das Feld \"0.0\" ein.","key":"_#_platform_#_.cost.click","type":"text","default":"0.0","verify":"float","cssClasses":["autoWidth"],"rightlabel":"const(DEFAULT_CURRENCY)","formatstr":"%.2f"},"campaign":{"label":"Kampagnenlink","desc":"Um ein Kapagnenlink anzulegen, der sich speziell nachverfolgen l&auml;sst, geben Sie bitte eine Zeichenkette ohne \n\t\t\t\t           Sonderzeichen (z. B. Umlaute, Interpunktionszeichen und Leerzeichen) ein, wie zum Beispiel \"allesmussraus\".","key":"_#_platform_#_.campaignlink","verify":"regex(\"[A-Za-z0-9]*\")","type":"text"}}},"price":{"headline":"Price Calculation","fields":{"whichprice":{"label":"Price Options","leftlabel":"Price from customer group","desc":"Here you can decide which group price will be used for the calculation of prices for eBay.<ul><li>If your shop system supports customer groups, you can define a dedicated group with prices for eBay - or use one of the groups already defined.<\/li><li>If a product doesn&apos;t have a group price defined, the main shop price is used.<\/li><li>Special prices are used (if the checkbox is active) regardless of the group prices.<\/li><\/ul>","key":"amazon.price.group","type":"selection","values":null,"cssClasses":["rightSpacer"],"morefields":{"cost":{"key":"amazon.price.usespecialoffer","type":"checkbox","values":{"val":"use special pricing"},"default":{"val":false}}}},"specialprices":{"label":"Special prices","desc":"Use also special offers \/ sale prices, if applicable","key":"amazon.price.usespecialoffer","type":"checkbox","values":{"val":"use special pricing"},"default":{"val":false}},"exchangerate":{"label":"Exchange Rate","desc":"<b>Generally:<\/b><br \/>\n\t\t\t\t\t<br \/>\n\t\t\t\t\tIf the currency of the web-shop differs from the marketplace currency, during the order import process and during product uploading, magnalister calculates accordingly to the web-shop default currency.<br \/>\n\t\t\t\t\tWhen importing marketplace orders, concerning the currency settings, magnalister simulates exactly the same behavior like the web-shop saves any frontend-orders.<br \/>\n\t\t\t\t\t<br \/>\n\t\t\t\t\t<b>Caution:<\/b><br \/>\n                    <br \/>\n\t\t\t\t\tBy activating this function here, <span style=\"color:red\">the currency settings in your web-shop will be updated and overwritten with the current Yahoo Finance exchange-rate.<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\tIn consequence, this <span style=\"color:red\">affects your foreign currency in the web-shop frontend.<\/span><br \/>\n\t\t\t\t\t<br \/>\n\t\t\t\t\tThe following magnalister functions trigger the exchange-rate update:<ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li>Order import<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li>Preparation of products<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li>Upload of products<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li>Synchronization of stock and prices<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/ul><br \/>\n\t\t\t\t\tIf an exchange-rate of a marketplace is not configured in the web-shop currency settings, magnalister will display an error message.<br \/>\n\t\t\t\t\t<b>Disclaimer:<\/b> RedGecko GmbH assumes no liability for the accuracy of the exchange rate. Please check the submitted values in your _#_platform_#_-Account.","key":"amazon.exchangerate","type":"checkbox","values":{"\tupdate":"Update exchange rate automatically"},"default":{"update":false}}}},"shipping":{"headline":"Versanddetails","desc":"Legt fest, mit welchen Versandeinstellungen die Produkte bei diesem Marketplace eingestellt werden sollen.","fields":{"country":{"label":"Versand nach","key":"_#_platform_#_.shipping.country","type":"selection","values":null},"method":{"label":"Versandkosten","desc":"Es wird zun&auml;chst versucht die Versandkosten aus der Versandmethode zu berechnen.\n\t\t\t\t\tFalls diese kein Ergebnis liefert wird der hier angegebene Wert verwendet.<br>\n\t\t\t\t\tBei Versandkostenmodul \"Pauschal\" wird ebenfalls der hier angegebene Wert verwendet.","key":"_#_platform_#_.shipping.method","type":"selection","values":null,"hint":"Beispiel: 6.70 (Ohne Angabe einer W&auml;hrung)","morefields":{"cost":{"label":"Versandkosten","key":"_#_platform_#_.shipping.cost","type":"text","default":"0.00","verify":"float","cssClasses":["autoWidth"],"rightlabel":"const(DEFAULT_CURRENCY)","formatstr":"%.2f"}}}}}}